agline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/br/title/81624009","overview":"Um elixir desperta os mortos-vivos em uma vila. Em meio ao terror, uma família em conflito precisa se unir e lutar para sobreviver enquanto a cidade entra em colapso."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"불사의 약","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/kr/title/81624009","overview":"검증되지 않은 신약으로 인해 마을에 좀비들이 퍼진다. 그러자 불화를 겪고 있던 한 가족은 고향 마을이 무너져가는 가운데 생존을 위해 힘을 합쳐 싸운다."},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"El elixir de la inmortalidad","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/es/title/81624009","overview":"Un elixir revive a los muertos en un pueblo. Una familia con conflictos internos deberá unir fuerzas y luchar para sobrevivir cuando su ciudad natal peligra."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"The Elixir","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/fr/title/81624009","overview":"Lorsqu'un élixir crée une horde de morts-vivants, une famille en proie à la discorde doit se serrer les coudes et lutter pour survivre à la destruction de son village."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"长生血战","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"一个关系不和的家庭经营着一家知名的草药公司。公司老板试图创新，研制一种新药水，结果却引发了丧尸疫情。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Thuốc trường sinh","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/vn/title/81624009","overview":"Một loại thuốc trường sinh giải phóng xác sống trong một ngôi làng. Giữa lúc quê nhà dần sụp đổ, một gia đình bất hòa buộc phải hợp sức chiến đấu để sống sót."},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"霊薬","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/jp/title/81624009","overview":"ある霊薬により、村にゾンビが大量発生。故郷が崩壊していくなか、険悪な関係の家族は生き延びるために結束して戦わざるを得なくなる。"},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"The Elixir","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/it/title/81624009","overview":"Un elisir scatena i morti viventi in un villaggio. Una famiglia ai ferri corti deve unire le forze e combattere per sopravvivere mentre la sua città natale crolla."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"Elixír","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/cz/title/81624009","overview":"Zázračný elixír probudí ve vesnici k životu všechny nemrtvé. Rozhádaná rodina proto musí spojit síly, aby tuhle apokalypsu přežila."},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"The Elixir","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/de/title/81624009","overview":"Durch ein Elixir werden Untote auf eine Kleinstadt losgelassen. Eine zerstrittene Familie muss inmitten des Kollapses ihrer Heimatstadt gemeinsam ums Überleben kämpfen."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"Eliksir","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/pl/title/81624009","overview":"Eksperymentalny eliksir wywołuje epidemię nieumarłych. Skłócona rodzina musi się zjednoczyć i walczyć o przetrwanie, gdy jej wiosce grozi zagłada."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"Az elixír","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/hu/title/81624009","overview":"Egy elixír felébreszti a halottakat egy faluban, ezért a széthullás szélén álló családnak össze kell fognia a túlélés reményében, miközben szülővárosuk összeomlik."},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"Elixirul","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/ro/title/81624009","overview":"Un elixir dezlănțuie morții vii într-un sat. O familie dezbinată trebuie să se unească și să lupte pentru supraviețuire, în timp ce orașul lor natal se prăbușește."},"name":"Română","iso_639_1":"ro","iso_3166_1":"RO","english_name":"Romanian"},{"data":{"title":"El elixir de la inmortalidad","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/mx/title/81624009","overview":"Un elixir reanima a los muertos en una aldea. Una familia en conflicto debe unirse y luchar por sobrevivir mientras su hogar colapsa."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Елексирът","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Дисфункционално семейство, което управлява известен бизнес с билкови лекарства. Собственикът на компанията се опитва да въведе иновации, създавайки нова отвара, която в крайна сметка предизвиква зомби огнище."},"name":"български език","iso_639_1":"bg","iso_3166_1":"BG","english_name":"Bulgarian"},{"data":{"title":"Эликсир","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/ru/title/81624009","overview":"Из-за некоего эликсира в деревне происходит восстание живых мертвецов. Теперь членам семьи, в которой царит разлад, придется объединиться ради борьбы за выживание."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"Ölümsüzlük İksiri","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/tr/title/81624009","overview":"Bir iksir yüzünden zombi salgınının patlak verdiği köyde yaşayan aile, aralarındaki anlaşmazlığa son vermek ve memleketleri yok olurken hayatta kalmak için iş birliği yapmalıdır."},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"長生血戰","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/tw/title/81624009","overview":"一帖藥竟引發喪屍肆虐村莊，這個感情不睦的家庭必須團結起來，奮力挺過家園崩壞的危機。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"长生血战","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/sg-zh/title/81624009","overview":"一瓶灵药唤醒了村庄里的亡灵，这个分歧重重的家庭必须团结一致，在家园崩溃时拼命求生。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"SG","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"الإكسير","runtime":116,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/sa/title/81624009","overview":"يحرر إكسير جحافل الموتى الأحياء في إحدى القُرى، فيتعين على عائلة، يعيش أفرادها في خلاف مع بعضهم بعضًا، التكاتف والقتال من أجل البقاء على قيد الحياة فيما تنهار بلدتهم."},"name":"العربية","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"SA","english_name":"Arabic"},{"data":{"title":"الإكسير","runtime":116,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/ae/title/81624009","overview":"يحرر إكسير جحافل الموتى الأحياء في إحدى القُرى، فيتعين على عائلة، يعيش أفرادها في خلاف مع بعضهم بعضًا، التكاتف والقتال من أجل البقاء على قيد الحياة فيما تنهار بلدتهم."},"name":"العربية","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"AE","english_name":"Arabic"},{"data":{"title":"長生血戰","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/hk/title/81624009","overview":"一帖藥竟引發喪屍肆虐村莊，這個感情不睦的家庭必須團結起來，奮力挺過家園崩壞的危機。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"The Elixir","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/dk/title/81624009","overview":"En eliksir resulterer i et udbrud af zombier en landsby. En stridende familie må forene sig og kæmpe for at overleve, mens deres hjemby kollapser."},"name":"Dansk","iso_639_1":"da","iso_3166_1":"DK","english_name":"Danish"},{"data":{"title":"The Elixir","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/fi/title/81624009","overview":"Eliksiiri muuttaa asukkaita eläviksi kuolleiksi. Ongelmaperheen on yhdistettävä voimansa ja taisteltava selviytyäkseen hengissä keskellä kotikaupunkinsa romahdusta."},"name":"suomi","iso_639_1":"fi","iso_3166_1":"FI","english_name":"Finnish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/nl/title/81624009","overview":"Door een elixer wordt een dorp plotseling bedreigd door ondoden. Een verdeelde familie moet de handen ineen slaan en vechten om te overleven terwijl hun dorp uiteenvalt."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"Eliksir","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/hr/title/81624009","overview":"U jednom se selu zbog eliksira probude svi nemrtvi. Sukobljena obitelj mora se ujediniti i boriti za preživljavanje dok njihov grad propada."},"name":"Hrvatski","iso_639_1":"hr","iso_3166_1":"HR","english_name":"Croatian"},{"data":{"title":"סם החיים","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/il/title/81624009","overview":"סם חיים משחרר את המתים-החיים בכפר. משפחה מסוכסכת מוכרחה להתאחד ולהילחם כדי לשרוד לאור קריסת העיירה שלהם."},"name":"עִבְרִית","iso_639_1":"he","iso_3166_1":"IL","english_name":"Hebrew"},{"data":{"title":"द एलिक्सिर","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/in-hi/title/81624009","overview":"एक जादुई औषधि गांव के मरे हुए लोगों को ज़िंदा कर देती है. एक परिवार जिसकी आपस में नहीं बनती, अब अपने मतभेद भुलाकर एकजुट होने को मजबूर है क्योंकि उनका कस्बा विनाश की ओर बढ़ रहा है."},"name":"हिन्दी","iso_639_1":"hi","iso_3166_1":"IN","english_name":"Hindi"},{"data":{"title":"L'élixir","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/ca-fr/title/81624009","overview":"Des zombies se déchaînent dans un village à cause d'un élixir. Des familles en conflit doivent s'unir pour combattre et survivre, alors que leur monde s'effondre."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"CA","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Το Ελιξίριο","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/gr/title/81624009","overview":"Ένα ελιξίριο ξυπνάει τους νεκρούς σε ένα χωριό. Μια δυσλειτουργική οικογένεια πρέπει να ενωθεί και να παλέψει για την επιβίωση καθώς όλα γύρω καταρρέουν."},"name":"ελληνικά","iso_639_1":"el","iso_3166_1":"GR","english_name":"Greek"},{"data":{"title":"O Elixir","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/pt/title/81624009","overview":"Um elixir solta uma horda de mortos-vivos numa aldeia. Uma família em conflito tem de se unir e lutar para sobreviver perante o colapso da sua terra natal."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Еліксир","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/ua/title/81624009","overview":"Еліксир спричиняє навалу нежиті. Сім’я, яка має негаразди в стосунках, мусить об’єднатися й боротися за виживання, доки її місто охоплює хаос."},"name":"Український","iso_639_1":"uk","iso_3166_1":"UA","english_name":"Ukrainian"},{"data":{"title":"The Elixir","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/no/title/81624009","overview":"En vidundermedisin er årsak til at en landsby angripes av vandøde. En splittet familie må komme sammen og kjempe for livet mens hjembyen deres ødelegges."},"name":"Norsk","iso_639_1":"no","iso_3166_1":"NO","english_name":"Norwegian"},{"data":{"title":"The Elixir","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/ph/title/81624009","overview":"Dahil sa isang elixir, nagsilabasan ang mga undead sa isang village. Kailangang magkaisa at makipaglaban ng isang pamilya habang gumuguho na ang hometown nila."},"name":"","iso_639_1":"tl","iso_3166_1":"PH","english_name":"Tagalog"},{"data":{"title":"The Elixir","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/se/title/81624009","overview":"Ett elixir får de döda att återuppstå i en indonesisk by, och en familj måste lägga sina konflikter åt sidan och samarbeta för att överleva medan samhället faller sönder runt dem."},"name":"svenska","iso_639_1":"sv","iso_3166_1":"SE","english_name":"Swedish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/my/title/81624009","overview":"Sejenis ubat mencetuskan wabak zombi di sebuah kampung. Sebuah keluarga yang berkelahi perlu bersatu dan berjuang untuk menyelamatkan diri tatkala kampung mereka musnah."},"name":"Bahasa melayu","iso_639_1":"ms","iso_3166_1":"MY","english_name":"Malay"}],"reviews_tmdb":[{"id":"68fabd3928716d0476853631","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/68fabd3928716d0476853631","author":"patient1","content":"This one is a trip almost immediately, and we get to see some shenanigans afoot. \r\nThis film is at the very least creative in some aspects and yet still follows the tropes of the genre. \r\nIt does have a cool and unique feature, I hope sci-fi fans will appreciate it.","created_at":"2025-10-23T23:41:45.457Z","updated_at":"2025-11-30T17:52:17.441Z","author_details":{"name":"","rating":6,"username":"patient1","avatar_path":null}},{"id":"68faea840f40e2ac415ddaf4","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/68faea840f40e2ac415ddaf4","author":"Deep Red","content":"there is no zombie in indonesia but kimo stamboel mixed local wisdom with zombie thats really interesting, the gore scene remind me to \"brain dead\" by peter jackson ❤️","created_at":"2025-10-24T02:55:00.646Z","updated_at":"2025-11-08T23:41:30.251Z","author_details":{"name":"Deep Red","rating":7,"username":"deepred","avatar_path":"/7ClTRlXuPxuaSep3PrpuwZR0GIL.jpg"}},{"id":"68fc2d96acf9fb8a9f2a9fb2","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/68fc2d96acf9fb8a9f2a9fb2","author":"Call Me Dunham","content":"This isn’t the first Indonesian zombie movie, but probably the most proper one so far. The thing is, it actually has a lot of potential to be something great — too bad the execution feels kinda shallow. It’s gory and artistically disturbing, the local culture vibes are there too. I just wish the Jamu thing was explored deeper, ‘cause that could’ve made it stand out instead of feeling like just another zombie flick.\r\n\r\nStill, I gotta say I like the character drama — they’re pretty complex. It’s just a shame it wasn’t handled better. With more natural dialogue and interactions, the emotional tension between the characters and their fight to survive could’ve hit harder. Would’ve made the movie feel less empty, you know?","created_at":"2025-10-25T01:53:26.080Z","updated_at":"2025-10-25T01:53:26.143Z","author_details":{"name":"Call Me Dunham","rating":7,"username":"Hamzah1905","avatar_path":null}},{"id":"691ad2c8b49ff3c41d6096ba","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/691ad2c8b49ff3c41d6096ba","author":"Dean","content":"Decent zombie movie. Good job Indonesia!","created_at":"2025-11-17T07:46:16.530Z","updated_at":"2025-11-17T07:46:16.615Z","author_details":{"name":"Dean","rating":7,"username":"Ditendra","avatar_path":"/pbZ9zJZEVYmtmjOZHPRvnnYxqYt.png"}}],"recommendations":[{"id":1197137,"adult":false,"title":"Black Phone 2","video":false,"overview":"Four years after escaping The Grabber, Finney Blake is struggling with his life after captivity. When his sister Gwen begins receiving calls in her dreams from the black phone and seeing disturbing visions of three boys being stalked at a winter camp, the siblings become determined to solve the mystery and confront a killer who has grown more powerful in death and more significant to them than either could imagine.","genre_ids":[27,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":17.4338,"vote_count":927,"poster_path":"/gFddBLQ8wj9M9O82iPzgX5KVNHz.jpg","release_date":"2025-10-15","vote_average":6.752,"backdrop_path":"/6zKjoOOb3OZnZuiHtQZn4Kd69Gq.jpg","original_title":"Black Phone 2","original_language":"en"},{"id":82992,"adult":false,"title":"Fast & Furious 6","video":false,"overview":"Hobbs has Dominic and Brian reassemble their crew to take down a team of mercenaries; Dominic unexpectedly gets sidetracked with facing his presumed deceased girlfriend, Letty.","genre_ids":[28,53,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.0789,"vote_count":11045,"poster_path":"/thSmnRdrzPBBospIOJjLZBReqzo.jpg","release_date":"2013-05-21","vote_average":6.814,"backdrop_path":"/oqxCzAO8sn1rSco2Pc19DlitgEn.jpg","original_title":"Fast & Furious 6","original_language":"en"},{"id":157350,"adult":false,"title":"Divergent","video":false,"overview":"In a world divided into factions based on personality types, Tris learns that she's been classified as Divergent and won't fit in. When she discovers a plot to destroy Divergents, Tris and the mysterious Four must find out what makes Divergents dangerous before it's too late.","genre_ids":[28,12,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":8.9022,"vote_count":13318,"poster_path":"/aNh4Q3iuPKDMPi2SL7GgOpiLukX.jpg","release_date":"2014-03-14","vote_average":6.909,"backdrop_path":"/bgkFOoXEQMRjKkCvgoj7smdGbuh.jpg","original_title":"Divergent","original_language":"en"},{"id":93456,"adult":false,"title":"Despicable Me 2","video":false,"overview":"Gru is recruited by the Anti-Villain League to help deal with a powerful new super criminal.","genre_ids":[16,35,10751],"media_type":"movie","popularity":9.3952,"vote_count":11851,"poster_path":"/5Fh4NdoEnCjCK9wLjdJ9DJNFl2b.jpg","release_date":"2013-06-26","vote_average":6.942,"backdrop_path":"/fOipappvgVtUbbHOtmCkHzcwJjC.jpg","original_title":"Despicable Me 2","original_language":"en"},{"id":150540,"adult":false,"title":"Inside Out","video":false,"overview":"When 11-year-old Riley moves to a new city, her Emotions team up to help her through the transition. Joy, Fear, Anger, Disgust and Sadness work together, but when Joy and Sadness get lost, they must journey through unfamiliar places to get back home.","genre_ids":[16,10751,12,18,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":16.5969,"vote_count":23190,"poster_path":"/2H1TmgdfNtsKlU9jKdeNyYL5y8T.jpg","release_date":"2015-06-17","vote_average":7.909,"backdrop_path":"/o3i6AfTcWAuNvzAUV3q5lOmi6Gx.jpg","original_title":"Inside Out","original_language":"en"},{"id":19995,"adult":false,"title":"Avatar","video":false,"overview":"In the 22nd century, a paraplegic Marine is dispatched to the moon Pandora on a unique mission, but beco