e":"Transformers","original_language":"en"},{"id":341174,"adult":false,"title":"Fifty Shades Darker","video":false,"overview":"When a wounded Christian Grey tries to entice a cautious Ana Steele back into his life, she demands a new arrangement before she will give him another chance. As the two begin to build trust and find stability, shadowy figures from Christian’s past start to circle the couple, determined to destroy their hopes for a future together.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":7.2835,"vote_count":7876,"poster_path":"/w3qa274gvca9t8pkUoG8nfQgTU3.jpg","release_date":"2017-02-08","vote_average":6.475,"backdrop_path":"/16aJtXO6lObbBUr11IvkjB1QD1f.jpg","original_title":"Fifty Shades Darker","original_language":"en"},{"id":49051,"adult":false,"title":"The Hobbit: An Unexpected Journey","video":false,"overview":"Bilbo Baggins, a hobbit enjoying his quiet life, is swept into an epic quest by Gandalf the Grey and thirteen dwarves who seek to reclaim their mountain home from Smaug, the dragon.","genre_ids":[12,14,28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":17.5154,"vote_count":19336,"poster_path":"/yHA9Fc37VmpUA5UncTxxo3rTGVA.jpg","release_date":"2012-12-12","vote_average":7.367,"backdrop_path":"/xyXmtuvsoM5J3yNad0nvcetpBdY.jpg","original_title":"The Hobbit: An Unexpected Journey","original_language":"en"},{"id":131634,"adult":false,"title":"The Hunger Games: Mockingjay - Part 2","video":false,"overview":"As the war between the Capitol and the districts reaches its peak, Katniss Everdeen embarks on a perilous mission to liberate Panem and confront President Snow. Joined by a team of trusted allies, she navigates deadly traps, shifting loyalties, and the heavy cost of rebellion, determined to bring freedom to her people and end the Hunger Games once and for all.","genre_ids":[28,12,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":7.6525,"vote_count":13162,"poster_path":"/lImKHDfExAulp16grYm8zD5eONE.jpg","release_date":"2015-11-18","vote_average":6.901,"bac