cked. While M faces challenges to her authority and position from Gareth Mallory, the new Chairman of the Intelligence and Security Committee, it's up to Bond, aided only by field agent Eve, to locate the mastermind behind the attack.","genre_ids":[28,12,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":8.9258,"vote_count":15921,"poster_path":"/d0IVecFQvsGdSbnMAHqiYsNYaJT.jpg","release_date":"2012-10-24","vote_average":7.257,"backdrop_path":"/qB2eFmGEh5YCzhXUpz7As2PaDCh.jpg","original_title":"Skyfall","original_language":"en"},{"id":24428,"adult":false,"title":"The Avengers","video":false,"overview":"When an unexpected enemy emerges and threatens global safety and security, Nick Fury, director of the international peacekeeping agency known as S.H.I.E.L.D., finds himself in need of a team to pull the world back from the brink of disaster. Spanning the globe, a daring recruitment effort begins!","genre_ids":[878,28,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":50.5441,"vote_count":36098,"poster_path":"/RYMX2wcKCBAr24UyPD7xwmjaTn.jpg","release_date":"2012-04-25","vote_average":7.951,"backdrop_path":"/pGFQCp12a8andfPlpnmXz44IIvY.jpg","original_title":"The Avengers","original_language":"en"},{"id":680,"adult":false,"title":"Pulp Fiction","video":false,"overview":"A burger-loving hit man, his philosophical partner, a drug-addled gangster's moll and a washed-up boxer converge in this sprawling, comedic crime caper. Their adventures unfurl in three stories that ingeniously trip back and forth in time.","genre_ids":[53,80,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":22.3091,"vote_count":29739,"poster_path":"/vQWk5YBFWF4bZaofAbv0tShwBvQ.jpg","release_date":"1994-09-10","vote_average":8.486,"backdrop_path":"/96hiUXEuYsu4tcnvlaY8tEMFM0m.jpg","original_title":"Pulp Fiction","original_language":"en"},{"id":118340,"adult":false,"title":"Guardians of the Galaxy","video":false,"overview":"Light years from Earth, 26 years after being abducted, Peter Quill finds himself the prime target of a manhunt after discovering an orb wanted by Ronan the Accuser.","genre_ids":[28,878,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":10.3704,"vote_count":29354,"poster_path":"/r7vmZjiyZw9rpJMQJdXpjgiCOk9.jpg","release_date":"2014-07-30","vote_average":7.905,"backdrop_path":"/vmBSlRZYKfNdaDZ7wGkrSNbmdMI.jpg","original_title":"Guardians of the Galaxy","original_language":"en"},{"id":76757,"adult":false,"title":"Jupiter Ascending","video":false,"overview":"In a universe where human genetic material is the most precious commodity, an impoverished young Earth woman becomes the key to strategic maneuvers and internal strife within a powerful dynasty…","genre_ids":[878,14,28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":7.6786,"vote_count":7010,"poster_path":"/2NCcAZ3M3F0FxENYmammBknwpVn.jpg","release_date":"2015-02-04","vote_average":5.456,"backdrop_path":"/w4hk4QG05nDuSgimpa7XAM6OyPX.jpg","original_title":"Jupiter Ascending","original_language":"en"}],"similar_content":[{"id":59,"adult":false,"title":"A History of Violence","video":false,"overview":"An average family is thrust into the spotlight after the father commits a seemingly self-defense murder at his diner.","genre_ids":[18,53,80],"popularity":2.9401,"vote_count":3616,"poster_path":"/3qnO72NHmUgs9JZXAmu4aId9QDl.jpg","release_date":"2005-09-23","vote_average":7.164,"backdrop_path":"/iZHJsUYxhjI6kbooHoQRWXv6F8E.jpg","original_title":"A History of Violence","original_language":"en"},{"id":74,"adult":false,"title":"War of the Worlds","video":false,"overview":"Ray Ferrier is a divorced dockworker and less-than-perfect father. Soon after his ex-wife and her new husband drop off his teenage son and young daughter for a rare weekend visit, a strange and powerful lightning storm touches down.","genre_ids":[12,53,878],"popularity":9.6095,"vote_count":8977,"poster_path":"/6Biy7R9LfumYshur3YKhpj56MpB.jpg","release_date":"2005-06-28","vote_average":6.531,"backdrop_path":"/bInicBgSHfQiWLbnRT5jxw9Grvm.jpg","original_title":"War of the Worlds","original_language":"en"},{"id":106,"adult":false,"title":"Predator","video":false,"overview":"A team of elite commandos on a secret mission in a Central American jungle come to find themselves hunted by an extraterrestrial warrior.","genre_ids":[878,28,12,53],"popularity":15.1628,"vote_count":8869,"poster_path":"/k3mW4qfJo6SKqe6laRyNGnbB9n5.jpg","release_date":"1987-06-12","vote_average":7.544,"backdrop_path":"/otkJlfjB7zJ5h34FEIfemenMbCy.jpg","original_title":"Predator","original_language":"en"},{"id":154,"adult":false,"title":"Star Trek II: The Wrath of Khan","video":false,"overview":"The starship Enterprise and its crew is pulled back into action when old nemesis, Khan, steals a top secret device called Project Genesis.","genre_ids":[28,12,878,53],"popularity":3.5314,"vote_count":2077,"poster_path":"/uPyLsKl8Z0LOoxeaFXsY5MxhR5s.jpg","release_date":"1982-06-04","vote_average":7.446,"backdrop_path":"/meqmvZjKpQ7WRhpZvIoKIAvioSD.jpg","original_title":"Star Trek II: The Wrath of Khan","original_language":"en"},{"id":170,"adult":false,"title":"28 Days Later","video":false,"overview":"Twenty-eight days after a killer virus was accidentally unleashed from a British research facility, a small group of London survivors are caught in a desperate struggle to protect themselves from the infected. Carried by animals and humans, the virus turns those it infects into homicidal maniacs -- and it's absolutely impossible to contain.","genre_ids":[27,53,878],"popularity":17.7462,"vote_count":8255,"poster_path":"/sQckQRt17VaWbo39GIu0TMOiszq.jpg","release_date":"2002-10-31","vote_average":7.236,"backdrop_path":"/aJFwk1clMal1prxAvKAgHxKPAf.jpg","original_title":"28 Days Later","original_language":"en"},{"id":463065,"adult":false,"title":"Still","video":false,"overview":"Still is a 5min dark zombie comedy that tells the story of 'Statue', a living statue entertainer caught up in the middle of a zombie outbreak. He finds himself frozen in fear whilst everyone around him flees or dies at the hands of the attacking zombie horde. Left alone by the unknowing zombies in an large open square surrounded on all sides he has to rely on his amazing ability to stand very still to try work out a way to survive his ordeal.","genre_ids":[35,27],"popularity":0.1686,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":"/l24KeDpfPcEULEb9nE2HHIHpCrL.jpg","release_date":"2016-10-26","vote_average":7.3,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Still","original_language":"en"},{"id":186,"adult":false,"title":"Lucky Number Slevin","video":false,"overview":"Slevin is mistakenly put in the middle of a personal war between the city’s biggest criminal bosses. Under constant watch, Slevin must try not to get killed by an infamous assassin and come up with an idea of how to get out of his current dilemma.","genre_ids":[18,53,80,9648],"popularity":4.4273,"vote_count":4366,"poster_path":"/x21s3p5wPww534nYj1cWakTcqz4.jpg","release_date":"2006-02-24","vote_average":7.477,"backdrop_path":"/ShDHEWiJ4NL6ldn4W2m3bEkIBr.jpg","original_title":"Lucky Number Slevin","original_language":"en"},{"id":1452725,"adult":false,"title":"Ossa Crucis","video":false,"overview":"Detective Alan Pierce investigates the killings of a killer named “Ossa Crucis” as he delves deeper into the case he learns that perhaps there is more to this case than he thought.","genre_ids":[27,53,9648],"popularity":0.2259,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/dRKRwgeifb49jY5tfkCjjmFqVL7.jpg","release_date":"2025-03-22","vote_average":10,"backdrop_path":"/23oYszGcc4cJmkY6SfrE2MO8AL2.jpg","original_title":"Ossa Crucis","original_language":"en"},{"id":465177,"adult":false,"title":"Berserkers","video":false,"overview":"The film follows Zeke (Robert McMurray), Callie (Alicia Marie Marcucci), Les (Seth Gontkovic) and Hunter (Jake Mulliken) on the eve of Hunter's 29th birthday as they share in a few drinks on a seemingly dull day in their hometown of Somerset. The day takes a turn for the worse as everyone they have ever known are suddenly transformed into aggressively murderous flesh eating freaks. The four comrades are forced to hack and slash their way through the reanimated corpses of their closest friends and loved ones, only to find themselves on the precipice of a post apocalyptic wasteland littered with monsters and the looming threat of their fellow survivors.","genre_ids":[27,35],"popularity":1.6136,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":"/xRtyCI1AcI2igXC0rX2pzm0j1b5.jpg","release_date":"2014-08-16","vote_average":3.3,"backdrop_path":"/4CKWB9SHod2ezNaNlw2jnb9ZNnB.jpg","original_title":"Meltdown","original_language":"en"},{"id":1647,"adult":false,"title":"The Recruit","video":false,"overview":"A brilliant CIA trainee must prove his worth at the Farm, the agency's secret training grounds, where he learns to watch his back and trust no one.","genre_ids":[28,53],"popularity":1.7226,"vote_count":1866,"poster_path":"/xInKytrHV3EJeCAulOpn5Q0bMxh.jpg","release_date":"2003-01-31","vote_average":6.4,"backdrop_path":"/bwDTWOd0SCFWfRw8ophhykOgUBS.jpg","original_title":"The Recruit","original_language":"en"},{"id":1683,"adult":false,"title":"The Reaping","video":false,"overview":"Katherine Morrissey, a former Christian missionary, lost her faith after the tragic deaths of her family. Now she applies her expertise to debunking religious phenomena. When a series of biblical plagues overrun a small town, Katherine arrives to prove that a supernatural force is not behind the occurrences, but soon finds that science cannot explain what is happening. Instead, she must regain her faith to combat the evil that waits in a Louisiana swamp.","genre_ids":[27],"popularity":1.6819,"vote_count":878,"poster_path":"/o8Vl4Vxp5LBth9J6Aa3k6PAefxt.jpg","release_date":"2007-04-04","vote_average":5.748,"backdrop_path":"/4eakTJuJD3sRGfv1qVWW46iPq82.jpg","original_title":"The Reaping","original_language":"en"},{"id":1694,"adult":false,"title":"Re-Animator","video":false,"overview":"Conducting clandestine experiments within the morgue at Miskatonic University, scientist Herbert West reveals to a fellow graduate student his groundbreaking work concerning the re-animation of fresh corpses.","genre_ids":[878,35,27],"popularity":2.8838,"vote_count":1636,"poster_path":"/1hY6AUl92cL9GdZx031UWFiGETt.jpg","release_date":"1985-10-18","vote_average":7.048,"backdrop_path":"/ogojPeWqjHBVUGCPGhfMxyQJLZ7.jpg","original_title":"Re-Animator","original_language":"en"},{"id":1254624,"adult":false,"title":"Night Always Comes","video":false,"overview":"Facing eviction in a city her family can no longer afford, a woman plunges into a desperate and increasingly dangerous all-night search to raise $25,000.","genre_ids":[53,18,80],"popularity":15.893,"vote_count":246,"poster_path":"/1jDo1nG7rtjaaQGpr6e73x9i9Xp.jpg","release_date":"2025-08-15","vote_average":6.061,"backdrop_path":"/cVqQdzqo0ymSFJqU87bIiHV8bA7.jpg","original_title":"Night Always Comes","original_language":"en"},{"id":1061189,"adult":false,"title":"Undead Cemetery","video":false,"overview":"Eisuke Kasahara (47 years old), the director of surgery at Eiai University Hospital, is affectionate with his flashy wife Lisa (35 years old), who does not do housework for Roku, and asks a detective agency to investigate and discovers that Lisa is having an affair with her host. Eisuke tried to pressure Lisa for a divorce by confronting her with photographic evidence and an investigation report. However, on the contrary, Lisa confronts her with the results of an investigation that Eisuke is having an affair with Aki Nogami, a 24-year-old beautiful nurse. \"I'm a generous wife, so I don't make a fuss about my husband's infidelity, and of course I don't want to divorce him. However, if you really want to break up, I'll get plenty of alimony,\" Eisuke, who was threatened by Lisa, unilaterally says goodbye to Aki and chooses the path of remarriage with Lisa. But from here, Eisuke's real shambles awaited...","genre_ids":[27],"popularity":1.3906,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/zhGAyM7vuC27k2SMiL59hfwxWfX.jpg","release_date":"2014-06-20","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":"/94exEJEz2njDlqy9dOkqnEFEZ49.jpg","original_title":"アンデッド・セメタリー","original_language":"ja"},{"id":1635,"adult":false,"title":"The Island","video":false,"overview":"In 2019, Lincoln Six-Echo is a resident of a seemingly \"Utopian\" but contained facility. Like all of the inhabitants of this carefully-controlled environment, Lincoln hopes to be chosen to go to The Island — reportedly the last uncontaminated location on the planet. But Lincoln soon discovers that everything about his existence is a lie.","genre_ids":[28,53,878,12],"popularity":6.5305,"vote_count":5762,"poster_path":"/9MaZYEyFmQwNeDTxZGQEN8E0e4p.jpg","release_date":"2005-07-21","vote_average":6.689,"backdrop_path":"/zZZ1FDl5FPClZ9OnMrlaPA4Iuxv.jpg","original_title":"The Island","original_language":"en"},{"id":1637,"adult":false,"title":"Speed","video":false,"overview":"Tensions run high when a crazed bomber rigs a Los Angeles bus with a device that will kill everyone on board if the vehicle's speed dips below fifty miles per hour.","genre_ids":[28,53],"popularity":5.8408,"vote_count":6703,"poster_path":"/82PkCE4R95KhHICUDF7G4Ly2z3l.jpg","release_date":"1994-06-09","vote_average":7.147,"backdrop_path":"/lywmuPU5Hr1Mnpb9UGeDbILmkTx.jpg","original_title":"Speed","original_language":"en"},{"id":1991,"adult":false,"title":"Death Proof","video":false,"overview":"Austin's hottest DJ, Jungle Julia, sets out into the night to unwind with her two friends Shanna and Arlene. Covertly tracking their moves is Stuntman Mike, a scarred rebel leering from behind the wheel of his muscle car, revving just feet away.","genre_ids":[28,53],"popularity":3.6374,"vote_count":5510,"poster_path":"/vtu6H4NWnQVqEp3aanUq3hNeeot.jpg","release_date":"2007-05-22","vote_average":6.841,"backdrop_path":"/qbVCChwbGWDAgsCXKZxyjBrRiWx.jpg","original_title":"Death Proof","original_language":"en"},{"id":1992,"adult":false,"title":"Planet Terror","video":false,"overview":"Two doctors find their graveyard shift inundated with townspeople ravaged by sores. Among the wounded is Cherry Darling, a dancer whose leg was ripped from her body. As the invalids quickly become enraged aggressors, Cherry and her ex-boyfriend El Wray lead a team of accidental warriors into the night.","genre_ids":[27,28,53],"popularity":3.4735,"vote_count":3749,"poster_path":"/3705GxG0RN9XDV5y9IiXKYHw1fK.jpg","release_date":"2007-04-06","vote_average":6.684,"backdrop_path":"/iZBUOcku0xv9MMfiEMXiDqErPXl.jpg","original_title":"Planet Terror","original_language":"en"},{"id":1948,"adult":false,"title":"Crank","video":false,"overview":"Chev Chelios, a hit man wanting to go straight, lets his latest target slip away. Then he awakes the next morning to a phone call that informs him he has been poisoned and has only an hour to live unless he keeps adrenaline coursing through his body while he searches for an antidote.","genre_ids":[28,53,80],"popularity":5.3301,"vote_count":4114,"poster_path":"/bbGOV9lES80el46Hj4GLj5zY25F.jpg","release_date":"2006-08-31","vote_average":6.652,"backdrop_path":"/8JPz1636hMcaADngF4H4KOxXfp1.jpg","original_title":"Crank","original_language":"en"},{"id":1958,"adult":false,"title":"8 Women","video":false,"overview":"Eight women gather to celebrate Christmas in a snowbound cottage, only to find the family patriarch dead with a knife in his back. Trapped in the house, every woman becomes a suspect, each having her own motive and secret.","genre_ids":[35,53,9648],"popularity":1.9996,"vote_count":1049,"poster_path":"/bJu4Gm7NQb2woPiIovrPD5jNWzf.jpg","release_date":"2002-02-06","vote_average":6.904,"backdrop_path":"/6TmdYhlnM7OEITeuzcrX8XVlnp2.jpg","original_title":"8 femmes","original_language":"fr"}],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt32643830","twitter_id":null,"facebook_id":null,"wikidata_id":"Q136385500","instagram_id":null,"metacritic_id":"movie/the-elixir","rotten_tomatoes_id":"m/the_elixir"},"social_ids":{"twitter":null,"facebook":null,"instagram":null},"gdvg_id":148470,"wi